mes the sun</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span>                 <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E7\">E7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">  Here comes the sun and I say</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">  It's all right</span>\n\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">[Segunda Parte]</span>\n\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">  Little darling</span>\n              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span>              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7\">A7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">The smiles returning to the faces</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">  Little darling</span>\n               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span>                     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7\">A7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">It seems like years since it's been here</span>\n\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">[Refrão]</span>\n\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">  Here comes the sun</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span>                 <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E7\">E7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">  Here comes the sun and I say</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">  It's all right</span>\n\n( <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7\">A7</span> )\n\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">[Ponte]</span>\n\n( <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F\">F</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C\">C</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G/B\">G/B</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7\">A7</span> )\n\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">[Tab - Ponte]</span>\n\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Parte 1 de 6</span>\n           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord